<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>A minimal valid HTML5 document</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --blue: #323158;
      --gray: #f1f1f1;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background-color: var(--blue);
      color: white;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    #layout {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    header {
      background-color: var(--gray);
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    main {
      margin: 0 0.5em;
    }
    #main {
      border: 1px solid red;
      max-width: 30em;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    @media (min-width: 800px) and (orientation: landscape) {
      #layout {
        flex-direction: row;
        height: 100vh;
      }
      header {
        flex: 1;
        max-width: 500px;
      }
      main {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }
      #main {
        margin: 0 1.5em;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <div id="layout">
    <header>
      <h1 style="border: 1px solid green">
        <img
          src="/images/hello-yoga-800-original-transparent.png"
          alt="hello YOGA"
          width="800"
          height="800"
          style="max-width: 60%; max-height: 75vh; width: auto; height: auto"
        />
      </h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <div id="main">
        <h2>Mikey</h2>
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent
          pharetra quam tristique, tristique velit vel, laoreet est. Morbi
          imperdiet nisi ut aliquet congue.
        </p>
        <p>
          In id tempus urna. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per
          conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. Nunc quis nisl id quam
          pharetra scelerisque sed non ante. Aliquam tincidunt nulla id enim
          eleifend, blandit finibus sapien commodo. Duis cursus dolor in eros
          porttitor, eu ultrices quam malesuada.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</html>
